Brace yourselves everyone, Skolopad says her mom is ready to join the Twitter streets. And judging by the controversial dancer’s timeline, she is more stressed than we are about it. “Am I day dreaming? My mom wants a Twitter account,” Skolopad tweeted. The singer and dancer’s fans also advised her that allowing her mom to join Twitter is definitely a bad idea. We guess that her fans are worried about everything that Skolopad’s mom will discover about her daughter if she learns how to use the internet. But it seems as though Skolopad has convinced her mom to stick to Whatsapp, for now. “I told her Twitter opens only on Sundays,” Skolopad said.  